    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for someone looking for a practical daily driver. Mechanically, it starts and runs well, though it has high mileage and some expected wear on the suspension components. The exterior features several visible scratches and a few small door dings, while the interior shows some staining on the upholstery and wear on the steering wheel. It has been recently serviced with an oil change, but a new owner should anticipate some minor maintenance items in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that gets the job done without the premium price tag of a newer model.",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
